Prompt Test Macro
Presents a test prompt and message to verify the popup flow.

; First prompt uses the default Resume/Cancel UI.
%msg (Press Resume or Cancel to confirm default behaviour.)
M0 (Ensure the default Resume/Cancel prompt appears.)
%wait

; Second prompt exercises the custom title + button syntax.
PROMPT [title(Custom Choice)] Pick an option from the custom buttons. [btn(Option One)a] [btn(Option Two)b] [btn(Option Three)c]
%msg (Selected option key: [macro.prompt_choice_key] (label: [macro.prompt_choice_label]) index [macro.prompt_index])
%wait

; Third popup echoes the chosen option.
PROMPT [title(Choice Made)] Your choice was: [macro.prompt_choice_key] [btn(OK)]
%wait

; Additional prompt to show Cancel handling remains at the end.
M5
